title: Documentation
description: To get started with using your software, product or service was there documentation supplied.

title: Quality of Support
description: After you were onboarded how easy was it for you to access the Customer Support team? Supplied information via Human or AI to solve your problem.

title: Error Management
description: How well does the system or service manage errors. Is there data backup, what is the protocol for when things go off line.

title: Onboarding Experience
description: This is either via a human or software, how was the experience during choosing and purchasing the product, software or service. Was it easy to get started.

title: Brand Customisation
description: This feature allows for customisation to match the user's brand
